<h2>Register your vehicle</h2>

<p>If we don't hold details for a vehicle registered outside the UK, we won't know if it meets the standards. You need to register this vehicle with our partner EPC plc if you believe it meets the required ULEZ and/or LEZ standard.</p>

<p>This may take up to 10 working days.</p>
</div>
 
