    </div>
</div> 
 
</div>
 <div>

<h3>Until your registration is processed</h3>

<p>Until you register and prove your vehicle meets the standards, you'll need to pay the charges to drive in London. You can apply for a refund after your status has been confirmed.</p>
</div>
 
<div class="module-grid clearfix">
