 <div>

<h2>Direct Vision Standard (DVS) HGV Safety Permit</h2>

<p>All HGVs over 12 tonnes gross vehicle weight need to hold an HGV Safety Permit to prove they meet the Direct Vision Standard.</p>

<p>If you drive an HGV in Greater London at any time without a valid permit, you may receive a penalty charge notice (PCN).</p>

<p>If you don't have a permit for your vehicle&nbsp;you can <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/dvs-safety-permit-application/">apply for one online</a>.</p>
</div>
 
      
        
          
        
      
    
